       MonsterGraphic live, so a pure-data JobData patch is the whole v1.1 mod)
    2. Does the Goblin still LOOK like a Goblin? (-> rendering does not consume
       JobData.MonsterGraphic; PSX decomp says the only gameplay reader is the check)
  Run WITHOUT the main Beast Tamer mod (formulas must be vanilla 0x5A-0x5D so the
  check is actually exercised), WITH the TestKit for ability access.
-->

